attributes.imdb: http://www.imdb.com/name/nm3091498/'''Lara Pulver''' (born 1 September 1980) is an English actress. She is known for her roles in the television series ''Robin Hood'', ''True Blood'', ''Spooks'', ''Sherlock'', ''Skins: Fire'', ''Da Vinci's Demons'' and ''Fleming: The Man Who Would Be Bond'' and the film ''Edge of Tomorrow''.In ''Game of Thrones: A Telltale Games Series'', she voices Lady Elissa Forrester.==Credits==Telltale Game Series Credits
